        public static String getHostname(@NonNull

                                 @NonNull
                                 DNS.ServerType serverType)
                          throws UnknownHostException
        Get the configured hostname for a given ServerType. Gets the default hostname if not specified in the configuration.
        Parameters:
        conf - Configuration to look up.
        serverType - ServerType to look up in the configuration for overrides.
